Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:12.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:18.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:23.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:29.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
