Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:39.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:47.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:52.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:55.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
