Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:09.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:15.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
